# References

Butler, D. G., Cullis, B. R., Gilmour, A. R., Gogel, B. J., &
Thompson, R. (2017). *ASReml-R reference manual* (Version 4). VSN
International.

Gilmour, A. R., Cullis, B. R., & Verbyla, A. P. (1997). Accounting
for natural and extraneous variation in the analysis of field
experiments. *Journal of Agricultural, Biological, and Environmental
Statistics*, 2(3), 269–293.

Smith, A. B., Cullis, B. R., & Thompson, R. (2001). Analyzing
variety by environment data using multiplicative mixed models and
adjustments for spatial field trend. *Biometrics*, 57(4), 1138–1147.
